Hello all, my name is Messai Belayneh — I serve as the Director of Strategic Marketing and sit on the board for the Distant Relatives Project, a 501(c)(3) commited to creating opportunity and access to resources for underserved communities around the world. Our three core pillars include education, homelessness and health care. 

We’re currently developing a campaign to get PPE, including DIY masks and infrared thermometers, to Ethiopia. If there’s a team coordinating a similar initiative, i’d love to chat with the lead. 

Please let me know if I can be of assistance in any other efforts.

Best
